descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static-4.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/51560-1-1394395796.jpg[/img]
[b]DESCRIPTION
[/b]This is my custom enb preset made for the NLA weather mod, inspired by [url=http://kakasi-skyrim-modenb.blogspot.com.au/2014/06/skyrim-custom-enb.html]Kakasi[/url]'s unreleased enb. Bright days, murky nights, and dramatic sunrises. Has very strong and intensive depth of field. 

[b]REQUIRED[/b][b]
[/b]Obviously [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50065/?]Natural Lighting and Atmosphere

[/url][b]RECOMMENDED
[/b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61033/?]Perfect Water
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/212132/?]Pfuscher
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60220/?]Verdant
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32246/?]Ultimate Lush Overhaul[/url]
[b]
INSTALLATION
[/b]Drop give mod files in your skyrim folder, not your data folder 
Download ENB files [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0302.htm]Here
[/url]Put the d3d9.dll and the enbhost.exe in the same folder as my mod

[b]ENJOY
[/b]Have fun and please, send me your screenshots. My Steam: [url=http://steamcommunity.com/id/pm_]pm[/url] My Reddit: [url=https://www.reddit.com/user/Kanade35/]Kanade35[/url]

[b]CHANGE LOG
[/b]alpha2 - multiple performance patches, environmental tweaking, added enb sprites, and a few skylighting tweaks
alpha3 - multiple performance patches, removed additional enb sprites, dof tweaks
*added performance depth of field optional files
beta1 - coming soon!
